To run this program:
% ./controller <port number>

This controller supports:
- OpenFlow version 1.0
- [In progress] Arbitrary switch graphs, including loops and multiple switches
- [In progress] Broadcast packets traverse a MST
- [In progress] Unicast traffic follows the shortest path between the source and destination
- [In progress] Multicast traffic is treated as broadcast traffic
- [In progress] Dynamic topologies (e.g., links coming and going while the controller is running)
